    Lineare       & solo sign.      & 13056.61 \\
    MARS          & tutte (grado 1) & 12619.53 \\
    MARS          & tutte (grado 2) &  6596.50 \\
    GAM (splines) & tutte           & 12643.32 \\
    GAM (splines) & solo sign.      & 12998.99 \\
